    "body": "From my personal experience, this is a good thing at game start, so you can immediately start building, and gain a few seconds over your opponent. \r\n\r\nAlso, as you are talking about basepushing, you don't only drop basedefences, but also buildings, so it's not that bad.\r\n\r\nFinally, use hotkeys to quickly switch to whatever tab you like."
