    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I think this should change, this should not be a default action for a RTS game with a permanent display of queues. The purpose of the permanent queue is to be able to build when you are far away from the base.\r\n\r\nStarCraft does not have a permanent display and it makes sense to \"select\" the queue of the building.\r\n\r\nWill have a look at RA2"
